10 Downing Street]]. Event with members of the local Anglo-Portuguese community at the [[Embassy of Portugal, London|Portuguese embassy]].<ref name="UK2016">{{Cite news|url=http://observador.pt/2016/11/16/em-visita-oficial-a-londres-marcelo-rebelo-de-sousa-encontra-se-com-financeiros-e-primeira-ministra/|title=Em visita oficial a Londres, Marcelo Rebelo de Sousa encontra-se com financeiros e primeira-ministra|last=Lusa|first=Agência|newspaper=Observador|language=pt-PT|access-date=2016-11-16}}</ref> 17 November: Visit to artist [[Paula Rego]]'s workshop. Reception hosted by [[Elizabeth II|Queen Elizabeth II]].<ref name="UK2016"/> |}
