ataforma|access-date=2018-11-20|archive-url=https://www.plataformamedia.com/en-uk/news/politics/interior/marcelo-arrives-in-washington-today-for-official-visit-and-meeting-with-trump-9511995.html|archive-date=2018-11-20|language=pt-PT}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://portuguese-american-journal.com/diplomacy-president-rebelo-de-sousa-to-meet-president-donald-trump-washingtondc/|title=Diplomacy: President Rebelo de Sousa to meet President Donald Trump – Washington,DC - Portuguese American Journal|last=|first=|date=|website=portuguese-american-journal.com|archive-url=http://portuguese-american-journal.com/diplomacy-president-rebelo-de-sousa-to-meet-president-donald-trump-washingtondc/|archive-date=2018-11-20|dead-url=|access-date=2018-11-20}}</ref> |}
