'''Ngerkeai''' is a village in [[Babeldaob]] island, the largest island in the island nation of the Republic of [[Palau]]. The village is the administrative center of [[Ngiwal]] state of Palau.<ref>{{cite web |title=Palau Photo: Ngerkeai |url=https://www.tripadvisor.com/LocationPhotoDirectLink-g294135-i206395989-Palau.html |publisher=[[Tripadvisor]] |accessdate=11 July 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Ngerkeai, Palau |url=https://www.zeitverschiebung.net/en/city/4038014 |publisher=Time Difference |accessdate=11 July 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Average Weather in Ngerkeai Palau |url=https://weatherspark.com/y/143321/Average-Weather-in-Ngerkeai-Palau-Year-Round |publisher=Weather Spark |accessdate=11 July 2018}}</ref> 

